extends layout

block content
  .card
    h1 🎮 About Our Gaming Platform

    p
      | Welcome to our Gaming Community Platform! This project was built as part of our Sprint 4 coursework.

    h2 🚀 Features
    ul
      li User login and registration
      li Browse and search gaming posts
      li Filter posts by category and tags
      li Like and rate posts
      li Comment on posts
      li Create your own posts
      li View user profiles

    h2 👨‍💻 Our Team
    p
      | We are a group of 4 developers passionate about gaming and web development.

    h2 🎯 Our Goal
    p
      | To create a simple and interactive platform where users can share and explore gaming content.

    h2 📚 Technologies Used
    ul
      li Node.js & Express
      li MySQL Database
      li Pug Templates
      li Docker Containers
      li GitHub Actions CI/CD

    h2 ⚙️ DevOps
    p
      | Our application runs in Docker containers with an automated CI/CD pipeline using GitHub Actions that builds and tests the app on every push.